{"tid":2151922,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張劍虹: 「艱險我奮進，困乏我多情」、「公道自在人心」","createTime":"2020-08-11T15:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T16:42:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4faa3837a25adbaeca7222aefb6bb23c69eabeab","tid":2151922,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:53:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200811/AATTI3U4H6NGQ2ZCQW7XWZ5V6Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200811%2FAATTI3U4H6NGQ2ZCQW7XWZ5V6Q%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=6b89e8b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200811%2FAATTI3U4H6NGQ2ZCQW7XWZ5V6Q%2F&h=83fe2a2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200811/AATTI3U4H6NGQ2ZCQW7XWZ5V6Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n【23:09】壹傳媒行政總裁張劍虹被扣留逾30小時後，獲准以10萬元保釋，離開秀茂坪警署。他感謝香港讀者血肉長城保衞《蘋果日報》，強調《蘋果日報》會繼續努力，直言「艱險我奮進，困乏我多情」、「公道自在人心」。張劍虹1983年畢業於中大新傳學院，而「艱險我奮進，困乏我多情」則出自新亞校歌，由身兼國學大師的首任院長錢穆所作。"},{"pid":"4fe594b4ecd31880bfc29b9a60effcac7ed5a537","tid":2151922,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8f13404170aa742afcfa47da8a411f5ae963d5","tid":2151922,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:56:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由身兼國學大師的首任院長錢穆所作。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n錢穆專作扭曲歷史<br />\n<br />\n唔怪之得毒果班友咁鍾意發大中華花癲"},{"pid":"8009c749e683ff46d6518ca4a578eb33a92e6e16","tid":2151922,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr